title: Best of My Momma Told Me 2021 Part 1
itunes:title: Best of My Momma Told Me 2021 Part 1
description:
Join Langston as he goes through the best moments of My Momma Told Me which include the best homemade hoteps, white lies, and original games from all our wonderful guests including Laci Mosley, Michael Harriot, Shaun Diston, Bashir Salahuddin, and Alex English. There are so many that we are making this a 2-parter. Happy Holidays, B*tch!
